4 (5) "Juvenile detention facility" means a short-term detention center, a youth detention facility,
5 including a regional detention facility, or a secure detention facility that is under contract with the state or a
6 subdivision of the state.
7 (6) "Local domestic violence program" means a shelter or safe home for victims of domestic
